CoralOS Initial Ramdisk

This is the initial ramdisk for CoralOS, containing the basic system files and configuration needed to boot the system.

Directory structure:
/bin      - System binaries
/lib      - Shared libraries
/etc      - System configuration files

Files:
/bin/init  - System initialization script
/bin/help  - Help command
/etc/passwd - User account information
/etc/group  - Group information
/etc/fstab  - Filesystem mount information
/etc/hosts  - Hostname resolution
/etc/resolv.conf - DNS configuration
/etc/profile - Shell profile
/etc/inputrc - Readline configuration
/etc/bash.bashrc - Bash configuration
/etc/issue - Login prompt
/etc/motd - Message of the day 